  "content": "\n                <p>Persistent vegetative state (<span data-phrasegroup-id=\"SgVyuF0\" data-type=\"bonus\" class=\"api dictionary\" data-content=\"PHA+QW4gYWJicmV2aWF0aW9uIHRoYXQgY2FuIHJlZmVyIHRvOjxicj4NCjEuIFBlcnNpc3RlbnQgdmVnZXRhdGl2ZSBzdGF0ZTxicj4NCjIuIFBsdW1tZXItVmluc29uLVN5bmRyb21lPC9wPg==\" id=\"L178cd3ca878f2ec06fb13d38fba794ee\" data-source=\"L178cd3ca878f2ec06fb13d38fba794ee\">PVS</span>) is a clinical condition in which function of the cortex is impaired while function of the <span data-phrasegroup-id=\"NqX-A_\" class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Z147ea0a4bbdff4d78bc40bde59d23bed\" data-learningcard-id=\"b70H4h\" data-lxid=\"b70H4h\" data-title=\"QnJhaW5zdGVt\" id=\"Ld477a4ed183cde82486dd96ab1a5f44d\" data-source=\"Ld477a4ed183cde82486dd96ab1a5f44d\">brainstem</span> is preserved for a period of more than one month. <span data-phrasegroup-id=\"f-Yk97\" class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Zcbb9395695c64fa30a5062b9e647bd5b\" data-learningcard-id=\"eR0xNf\" data-lxid=\"eR0xNf\" data-title=\"VHJhdW1hdGljIGJyYWluIGluanVyeQ==\" id=\"Lbb19994e52a9191efd034f7787b07c52\" data-source=\"Lbb19994e52a9191efd034f7787b07c52\">Traumatic brain injury</span> and diffuse cerebral <span data-phrasegroup-id=\"GT0BH2\" class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Z11178ec3c2e582d07f19c0f784e018a3\" data-learningcard-id=\"ZI0ZYh\" data-lxid=\"ZI0ZYh\" data-section-id=\"5h1ieg0\" data-sxid=\"5h1ieg0\" data-title=\"UmVzcGlyYXRvcnkgcGh5c2lvbG9neSDihpIgUmVzcGlyYXRvcnkgcmVndWxhdGlvbg==\" id=\"L5c4cc9b57fbd665a83d3831235ddb373\" data-source=\"L5c4cc9b57fbd665a83d3831235ddb373\">hypoxia</span> are the most common etiologies. Patients in <span data-phrasegroup-id=\"SgVyuF0\" data-type=\"bonus\" class=\"api dictionary\" data-content=\"PHA+QW4gYWJicmV2aWF0aW9uIHRoYXQgY2FuIHJlZmVyIHRvOjxicj4NCjEuIFBlcnNpc3RlbnQgdmVnZXRhdGl2ZSBzdGF0ZTxicj4NCjIuIFBsdW1tZXItVmluc29uLVN5bmRyb21lPC9wPg==\" id=\"L78b240b275ad1adab24fdddb24bd942d\" data-source=\"L78b240b275ad1adab24fdddb24bd942d\">PVS</span> may appear awake but are not aware or conscious, and they are unable to communicate with others or purposefully interact with their environment. However, they are still able to breathe on their own, <span class=\"nowrap\">sleep-wake</span> cycles are preserved, and autonomic function is at least partially retained. <span data-phrasegroup-id=\"SgVyuF0\" data-type=\"bonus\" class=\"api dictionary\" data-content=\"PHA+QW4gYWJicmV2aWF0aW9uIHRoYXQgY2FuIHJlZmVyIHRvOjxicj4NCjEuIFBlcnNpc3RlbnQgdmVnZXRhdGl2ZSBzdGF0ZTxicj4NCjIuIFBsdW1tZXItVmluc29uLVN5bmRyb21lPC9wPg==\" id=\"Lf44fd09249518667bc4221029f7c7f16\" data-source=\"Lf44fd09249518667bc4221029f7c7f16\">PVS</span> is a <span data-phrasegroup-id=\"PWWWl40\" data-type=\"bonus\" class=\"api dictionary\" data-content=\"PHA+VGhlIGlkZW50aWZpY2F0aW9uIG9mIGEgZGlzZWFzZSBvciBjb25kaXRpb24gYmFzZWQgb24gdGhlIHBhdGllbnQncyBtZWRpY2FsIGhpc3RvcnkgYW5kIGV4YW1pbmF0aW9uIGZpbmRpbmdzLiBMYWJvcmF0b3J5LCBpbWFnaW5nLCBhbmQgaGlzdG9sb2d5IHN0dWRpZXMgbWF5IGNvbmZpcm0gYW4gdW5jZXJ0YWluIGNsaW5pY2FsIGRpYWdub3Npcy48L3A+\" id=\"L479d2135fb2287d1b7729acf03433d45\" data-source=\"L479d2135fb2287d1b7729acf03433d45\">clinical diagnosis</span>, and it is important to differentiate it from <span data-phrasegroup-id=\"9z0NEi\" class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Z300240fc327de796336a58a91de88a43\" data-learningcard-id=\"br0Hfh\" data-lxid=\"br0Hfh\" data-section-id=\"QN1uah0\" data-sxid=\"QN1uah0\" data-title=\"TWVudGFsIHN0YXR1cyBleGFtaW5hdGlvbiDihpIgU2Vuc29yaXVtIGFuZCBjb2duaXRpb24=\" id=\"Lb6cdc3299498d72ef8efecaada201d47\" data-source=\"Lb6cdc3299498d72ef8efecaada201d47\">coma</span> (no <span class=\"nowrap\">sleep-wake</span> cycles) and <span class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Zf36f0ff3d9e1182c65b2d69f4597bc2e\" data-learningcard-id=\"vP0AgT\" data-lxid=\"vP0AgT\" data-section-id=\"R8Xlm-\" data-sxid=\"R8Xlm-\" data-title=\"RGVhdGgg4oaSIEJyYWluIGRlYXRo\" id=\"L762e02df0bcf8c5a2d37f18407b000bd\" data-source=\"L762e02df0bcf8c5a2d37f18407b000bd\">brain death</span> (no <span class=\"nowrap\">sleep-wake</span> cycles or <span data-phrasegroup-id=\"NqX-A_\" class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Z147ea0a4bbdff4d78bc40bde59d23bed\" data-learningcard-id=\"b70H4h\" data-lxid=\"b70H4h\" data-title=\"QnJhaW5zdGVt\" id=\"L73366a59900faf95a845230eb206aefb\" data-source=\"L73366a59900faf95a845230eb206aefb\">brainstem</span> function). No definitive treatment exists. Although most patients remain in a vegetative state for years, a few may recover spontaneously. A vegetative state is declared permanent when recovery is very unlikely (i.e., <span data-phrasegroup-id=\"SgVyuF0\" data-type=\"bonus\" class=\"api dictionary\" data-content=\"PHA+QW4gYWJicmV2aWF0aW9uIHRoYXQgY2FuIHJlZmVyIHRvOjxicj4NCjEuIFBlcnNpc3RlbnQgdmVnZXRhdGl2ZSBzdGF0ZTxicj4NCjIuIFBsdW1tZXItVmluc29uLVN5bmRyb21lPC9wPg==\" id=\"L0731da4657fe230f36dac07503309f46\" data-source=\"L0731da4657fe230f36dac07503309f46\">PVS</span> due to trauma lasting more than <span class=\"nowrap\">1 year</span> or <span data-phrasegroup-id=\"SgVyuF0\" data-type=\"bonus\" class=\"api dictionary\" data-content=\"PHA+QW4gYWJicmV2aWF0aW9uIHRoYXQgY2FuIHJlZmVyIHRvOjxicj4NCjEuIFBlcnNpc3RlbnQgdmVnZXRhdGl2ZSBzdGF0ZTxicj4NCjIuIFBsdW1tZXItVmluc29uLVN5bmRyb21lPC9wPg==\" id=\"L7ebff1c993ec921ce5656fe605e832c7\" data-source=\"L7ebff1c993ec921ce5656fe605e832c7\">PVS</span> due to a nontraumatic cause lasting more than <span class=\"nowrap\">3 months</span>).</p>\n<ul>\n<li><span class=\"step-2-imppact2 imppact2 usmle-gs-imppact2 step-2-condensed\"><span class=\"step-1-imppact2 usmle-gs-imppact2 step-1-condensed\"><span class=\"wichtig\"><span class=\"linksuggest\"><span data-phrasegroup-id=\"f-Yk97\" class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Zcbb9395695c64fa30a5062b9e647bd5b\" data-learningcard-id=\"eR0xNf\" data-lxid=\"eR0xNf\" data-title=\"VHJhdW1hdGljIGJyYWluIGluanVyeQ==\" id=\"La93b12a97edd074f01af288e18341c3a\" data-source=\"La93b12a97edd074f01af288e18341c3a\">Traumatic brain injury</span></span></span></span></span></li>\n<li>\n<span class=\"step-2-imppact2 imppact2 usmle-gs-imppact2 step-2-condensed\"><span class=\"step-1-imppact2 usmle-gs-imppact2 step-1-condensed\"><span class=\"wichtig\">Diffuse cerebral <span data-phrasegroup-id=\"GT0BH2\" class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Z11178ec3c2e582d07f19c0f784e018a3\" data-learningcard-id=\"ZI0ZYh\" data-lxid=\"ZI0ZYh\" data-section-id=\"5h1ieg0\" data-sxid=\"5h1ieg0\" data-title=\"UmVzcGlyYXRvcnkgcGh5c2lvbG9neSDihpIgUmVzcGlyYXRvcnkgcmVndWxhdGlvbg==\" id=\"Lf30448181acf2754d15d978c0e6fe767\" data-source=\"Lf30448181acf2754d15d978c0e6fe767\">hypoxia</span></span></span></span><span class=\"condensed-hidden\"> </span><span class=\"condensed-hidden\"><span class=\"api explanation\" data-type=\"bonus\" data-content=\"\" id=\"E4cc9ee37f9da6f9f24ccb987d04edb00\"></span></span>\n</li>\n<li class=\"condensed-hidden\">Other causes of severe damage to the cerebral hemispheres and/or <span data-phrasegroup-id=\"ScXybC\" class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Zd64bfb19d2d1ca43c42b4d2c203deb2f\" data-learningcard-id=\"-60DnS\" data-lxid=\"-60DnS\" data-section-id=\"Fvcgbe0\" data-sxid=\"Fvcgbe0\" data-title=\"RGllbmNlcGhhbG9uIOKGkiBUaGFsYW11cw==\" id=\"L34b57afe1a95048b6c7f28f299c11eb9\" data-source=\"L34b57afe1a95048b6c7f28f299c11eb9\">thalamus</span> (e.g., <span data-phrasegroup-id=\"W5bPQ8\" class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Z2dee56e7d47fda8b04444494403b6eb8\" data-learningcard-id=\"v30A4f\" data-lxid=\"v30A4f\" data-section-id=\"IMaYJO\" data-sxid=\"IMaYJO\" data-title=\"TWFqb3IgbmV1cm9jb2duaXRpdmUgZGlzb3JkZXIg4oaSIEV0aW9sb2d5\" id=\"L98cc2959a03fd7c82eb5a460627bfac2\" data-source=\"L98cc2959a03fd7c82eb5a460627bfac2\">neurodegenerative diseases</span>, <span data-phrasegroup-id=\"6SXj0B\" class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Z0111aade770ed6f7d136b455de1d6c1f\" data-learningcard-id=\"lp0vpS\" data-lxid=\"lp0vpS\" data-section-id=\"1Cc2Ie0\" data-sxid=\"1Cc2Ie0\" data-title=\"TmVydmUgdGlzc3VlLCBzeW5hcHNlcywgYW5kIG5ldXJvdHJhbnNtaXR0ZXJzIOKGkiBOZXJ2ZSB0aXNzdWU=\" id=\"La74fcfb545ccc9dff916948a5cd261ed\" data-source=\"La74fcfb545ccc9dff916948a5cd261ed\">CNS</span> infections, metabolic disturbances, toxins, developmental <span data-phrasegroup-id=\"cHXa6z\" class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Za2917144496685a377f046c65f8f8102\" data-learningcard-id=\"vo0AdS\" data-lxid=\"vo0AdS\" data-section-id=\"f6ck4W0\" data-sxid=\"f6ck4W0\" data-title=\"RW1icnlvZ2VuZXNpcyDihpIgTW9ycGhvZ2VuZXNpcw==\" id=\"L3df9045e051444a3f949cb72c3ca2b29\" data-source=\"L3df9045e051444a3f949cb72c3ca2b29\">malformations</span> of the <span data-phrasegroup-id=\"6SXj0B\" class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Z0111aade770ed6f7d136b455de1d6c1f\" data-learningcard-id=\"lp0vpS\" data-lxid=\"lp0vpS\" data-section-id=\"1Cc2Ie0\" data-sxid=\"1Cc2Ie0\" data-title=\"TmVydmUgdGlzc3VlLCBzeW5hcHNlcywgYW5kIG5ldXJvdHJhbnNtaXR0ZXJzIOKGkiBOZXJ2ZSB0aXNzdWU=\" id=\"Lc101adb820f7911199411a2e4a86b9c2\" data-source=\"Lc101adb820f7911199411a2e4a86b9c2\">CNS</span>)</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"condensed-hidden\"><span class=\"unwichtig\">References:<span data-type=\"Reference\" data-eid=\"-PYDh6\" data-page=\"\" data-cmt=\"\" data-ref-index=\"1\">[1]</span></span></p>\n\n<p><span class=\"step-2-imppact2 imppact2 usmle-gs-imppact2 step-2-condensed\"><span class=\"step-1-imppact2 usmle-gs-imppact2 step-1-condensed\">Widespread damage to the <span class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Z6033c93dc0e1193696f0ff56b7d073a9\" data-learningcard-id=\"G60BmS\" data-lxid=\"G60BmS\" data-section-id=\"Nuc-rV0\" data-sxid=\"Nuc-rV0\" data-title=\"U3BpbmFsIGNvcmQgdHJhY3RzIGFuZCByZWZsZXhlcyDihpIgR3Jvc3MgYW5hdG9teQ==\" id=\"Le763a5e6f3594547403d6af5e28979d3\" data-source=\"Le763a5e6f3594547403d6af5e28979d3\">white matter</span> of both cerebral hemispheres and/or the <span data-phrasegroup-id=\"ScXybC\" class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Zd64bfb19d2d1ca43c42b4d2c203deb2f\" data-learningcard-id=\"-60DnS\" data-lxid=\"-60DnS\" data-section-id=\"Fvcgbe0\" data-sxid=\"Fvcgbe0\" data-title=\"RGllbmNlcGhhbG9uIOKGkiBUaGFsYW11cw==\" id=\"L35f30d4bc1af9b22c572c78e2ab2c5ba\" data-source=\"L35f30d4bc1af9b22c572c78e2ab2c5ba\">thalamus</span> bilaterally, <span class=\"wichtig\">without damage to the <span data-phrasegroup-id=\"NqX-A_\" class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Z147ea0a4bbdff4d78bc40bde59d23bed\" data-learningcard-id=\"b70H4h\" data-lxid=\"b70H4h\" data-title=\"QnJhaW5zdGVt\" id=\"L7191f459b51b81c9f2428d47672255f4\" data-source=\"L7191f459b51b81c9f2428d47672255f4\">brainstem</span></span></span></span><span class=\"condensed-hidden\">. This results in reduction of cortical function with preserved </span><span data-phrasegroup-id=\"NqX-A_\" class=\"api condensed-hidden\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Z147ea0a4bbdff4d78bc40bde59d23bed\" data-learningcard-id=\"b70H4h\" data-lxid=\"b70H4h\" data-title=\"QnJhaW5zdGVt\" id=\"Ldf6128c938d7f389f3a215c53286f47f\" data-source=\"Ldf6128c938d7f389f3a215c53286f47f\">brainstem</span><span class=\"condensed-hidden\"> control of respiration, cardiac function, </span><span class=\"nowrap condensed-hidden\">sleep-wake</span><span class=\"condensed-hidden\"> cycles, and reflexes.</span></p>\n<p class=\"condensed-hidden\"><span class=\"unwichtig\">References:<span data-type=\"Reference\" data-eid=\"Z4YZ36\" data-page=\"1327–1338\" data-cmt=\"\" data-ref-index=\"2\">[2]</span><span data-type=\"Reference\" data-eid=\"04Ye36\" data-page=\"\" data-cmt=\"\" data-ref-index=\"3\">[3]</span><span data-type=\"Reference\" data-eid=\"a4YQ36\" data-page=\"1037–1046\" data-cmt=\"\" data-ref-index=\"4\">[4]</span></span></p>\n\n<ul class=\"condensed-hidden-step1\">\n<li>\n<span class=\"step-2-imppact2 imppact2 usmle-gs-imppact2 step-2-condensed\">Usually preceded by <span data-phrasegroup-id=\"9z0NEi\" class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Z300240fc327de796336a58a91de88a43\" data-learningcard-id=\"br0Hfh\" data-lxid=\"br0Hfh\" data-section-id=\"QN1uah0\" data-sxid=\"QN1uah0\" data-title=\"TWVudGFsIHN0YXR1cyBleGFtaW5hdGlvbiDihpIgU2Vuc29yaXVtIGFuZCBjb2duaXRpb24=\" id=\"Lbf5141106c158d2a323ddaebc4e8c4a1\" data-source=\"Lbf5141106c158d2a323ddaebc4e8c4a1\">comatose</span> state</span><span class=\"condensed-hidden\"> requiring intensive care and gradual recovery of autonomic function </span><span class=\"condensed-hidden\"><span class=\"api explanation\" data-type=\"bonus\" data-content=\"\" id=\"Ee5bdccf06b9be01b5aefef1932bc5a55\"></span></span>\n</li>\n<li>But lack of recovery of higher mental function after <span class=\"nowrap\">1 month</span> and the following features:<ul>\n<li><span class=\"step-2-imppact2 imppact2 usmle-gs-imppact2 step-2-condensed\">Intact <span class=\"nowrap\">sleep-wake</span> cycles with periods of wakefulness</span></li>\n<li>\n<span class=\"step-2-imppact2 imppact2 usmle-gs-imppact2 step-2-condensed\"><span class=\"leitwort\">Loss of perceptual and <span class=\"nowrap\">self-awareness</span></span></span><ul class=\"condensed-hidden\">\n<li>Lack of purposeful response to external stimuli (e.g., tactile, auditory, visual, etc.)</li>\n<li>Inability to communicate and lack of apparent language comprehension</li>\n<li>Disconjugate <span class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Zf7048e7128eea53b75913aceae5813b3\" data-learningcard-id=\"cp0aoS\" data-lxid=\"cp0aoS\" data-section-id=\"YDcn1e0\" data-sxid=\"YDcn1e0\" data-title=\"RXllIGFuZCBvcmJpdCDihpIgRXh0cmFvY3VsYXIgbXVzY2xlcw==\" id=\"Lf4caa5197b72e2a2ce2ef29970923387\" data-source=\"Lf4caa5197b72e2a2ce2ef29970923387\">eye movements</span> with loss of fixation</li>\n<li>Occasional nonpurposeful limb movements and spontaneous smiling, crying, grunting, or screaming</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<span class=\"step-2-imppact2 imppact2 usmle-gs-imppact2 step-2-condensed\"><span class=\"leitwort\">Autonomic function and reflexes retained to variable degrees</span></span><ul class=\"condensed-hidden\">\n<li>Sufficient cardiovascular, respiratory, and <span data-phrasegroup-id=\"iU1J1T0\" data-type=\"bonus\" class=\"api dictionary\" data-content=\"PHA+VGhlIHByb2Nlc3MgYnkgd2hpY2ggdGhlIGJvZHkgbWFpbnRhaW5zIGEgY29uc2lzdGVudCBjb3JlIGJvZHkgdGVtcGVyYXR1cmUgZGVzcGl0ZSB2YXJpYXRpb25zIGluIGVudmlyb25tZW50YWwgdGVtcGVyYXR1cmUuIEZhY2lsaXRhdGVkIGJ5IGNoYW5nZXMgaW4gbWV0YWJvbGljIGFjdGl2aXR5IGFuZCBzd2VhdGluZy48L3A+\" id=\"Lb4f05a3122897af7f750da4871a22361\" data-source=\"Lb4f05a3122897af7f750da4871a22361\">thermoregulatory</span> function</li>\n<li>Sufficient <span data-phrasegroup-id=\"LBewYYa\" data-type=\"bonus\" class=\"api dictionary\" data-content=\"PHA+UmVsYXRpdm8gYWwgdHJhY3RvIGdhc3Ryb2ludGVzdGluYWwuPC9wPg==\" id=\"L687ccf175ac2f3d1472152bde60b532a\" data-source=\"L687ccf175ac2f3d1472152bde60b532a\">gastrointestinal</span> and renal function but bowel and <span data-phrasegroup-id=\"TN060g\" class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Z9228442e2f0b1e5f174aea00ba872821\" data-learningcard-id=\"ZQ0Zuf\" data-lxid=\"ZQ0Zuf\" data-title=\"VXJpbmFyeSBpbmNvbnRpbmVuY2U=\" id=\"L3a437e384659a47a2266d52226e02261\" data-source=\"L3a437e384659a47a2266d52226e02261\">bladder incontinence</span>\n</li>\n<li>Variable preservation of reflexes (e.g., <span data-phrasegroup-id=\"Tm16Uh0\" data-type=\"bonus\" class=\"api dictionary\" data-content=\"\" id=\"Ld3c52e6fdf075d8620e1dab682ee869b\" data-source=\"Ld3c52e6fdf075d8620e1dab682ee869b\">pupillary</span>, corneal, <span class=\"nowrap\">vestibulo-ocular</span>, gag, <span class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Z53178f74af701c6933574f4f111d6391\" data-learningcard-id=\"3L0Sxg\" data-lxid=\"3L0Sxg\" data-title=\"Q291Z2g=\" id=\"L8496c0c4e00cab056bd7acf6778205db\" data-source=\"L8496c0c4e00cab056bd7acf6778205db\">cough</span>)</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"condensed-hidden\"><span class=\"unwichtig\">References:<span data-type=\"Reference\" data-eid=\"Y4Yn36\" data-page=\"1499–1508\" data-cmt=\"\" data-ref-index=\"5\">[5]</span></span></p>\n<ul class=\"condensed-hidden-step1\">\n<li>\n<span class=\"step-2-imppact2 imppact2 usmle-gs-imppact2 step-2-condensed\"><span class=\"wichtig\"><span data-phrasegroup-id=\"PWWWl40\" data-type=\"bonus\" class=\"api dictionary\" data-content=\"PHA+VGhlIGlkZW50aWZpY2F0aW9uIG9mIGEgZGlzZWFzZSBvciBjb25kaXRpb24gYmFzZWQgb24gdGhlIHBhdGllbnQncyBtZWRpY2FsIGhpc3RvcnkgYW5kIGV4YW1pbmF0aW9uIGZpbmRpbmdzLiBMYWJvcmF0b3J5LCBpbWFnaW5nLCBhbmQgaGlzdG9sb2d5IHN0dWRpZXMgbWF5IGNvbmZpcm0gYW4gdW5jZXJ0YWluIGNsaW5pY2FsIGRpYWdub3Npcy48L3A+\" id=\"L7ba16e07600d7027dc72e59453234eec\" data-source=\"L7ba16e07600d7027dc72e59453234eec\">Clinical diagnosis</span></span></span><span class=\"condensed-hidden\"> based on </span><span class=\"wichtig condensed-hidden\"><span class=\"nowrap\">≥ 1 month</span></span><span class=\"condensed-hidden\"> of intact sleep-wake cycles, loss of perception and self-awareness, and autonomic functions retained to variable degrees</span>\n</li>\n<li class=\"condensed-hidden\">\n<span class=\"leitwort\"><span data-phrasegroup-id=\"vg1ACT0\" data-type=\"bonus\" class=\"api dictionary\" data-content=\"\" id=\"Lcab2ba9d583bd35056907e94dd6a92a4\" data-source=\"Lcab2ba9d583bd35056907e94dd6a92a4\">Neuroimaging</span></span><ul>\n<li>CT/<span data-phrasegroup-id=\"8n0OEg\" class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Zefb6206a3f821bf7e5942b654dc6f6cf\" data-learningcard-id=\"pN0LXg\" data-lxid=\"pN0LXg\" data-title=\"TWFnbmV0aWMgcmVzb25hbmNlIGltYWdpbmc=\" id=\"L3a4a327ce482c1687f3887926f205cfe\" data-source=\"L3a4a327ce482c1687f3887926f205cfe\">MRI</span>: nonspecific diffuse or multifocal abnormalities involving the <span data-phrasegroup-id=\"JoUs1Va\" data-type=\"bonus\" class=\"api dictionary\" data-content=\"PHA+TGEgdW5pZGFkIGRlbCBzaXN0ZW1hIGludGVybmFjaW9uYWwgZGUgZG9zaXMgZGUgcmFkaWFjacOzbi4gU2UgZXhwcmVzYSBjb21vIGxhIGNhbnRpZGFkIGRlIGVuZXJnw61hIGFic29yYmlkYSBwb3IgbWFzYSBkZSB0ZWppZG8gKHAuIGVqLiwg